plyTime":"2019-09-01T19:46:48.000Z","msg":"左膠不除 香港永無翻生之日"},{"pid":"d23e4a844b5896f6e96c10ba35fab0cf1b1be208","tid":1527280,"uid":140924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:54:45.000Z","msg":"終於有人肯講，左膠消失左一輪之後，到尋日起左個火之後全數出晒嚟，真係唔明個邏輯，打不還手以佔道德高地攞光環？咁你自己企出去用身擋槍擋刀先，成個光環送畀你又點話。"},{"pid":"86f6309af90e937b6928fb2e86a18400d9dd18b5","tid":1527280,"uid":60137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T19:59:12.000Z","msg":"麻煩前線以後連左膠都打埋，仲要打得大力啲"},{"pid":"09e987fe3126af18d21ca7bf1700b05f9851b65b","tid":1527280,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566abdd0fbbc5c401b70aa4b019723b0a85ac2af","tid":1527280,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:10:18.000Z","msg":"不割蓆，有時就係因為被藍屍感覺我吔太友善而經常有單人匹馬嚟生事。"},{"pid":"ca89f1d6f1bb5e1cbbbfe23bfdd26d2315e4f69f","tid":1527280,"uid":27804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:15:50.000Z","msg":"你而家係咪攬佢啊死老襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521893cd4dc110b3338c2646cfc71c34283e8b12","tid":1527280,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8193ae3179f80b94208ac364e02178ac71c5fa95","tid":1527280,"uid":137480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:46:00.000Z","msg":"左膠係敵對勢力,講用對付黑警同藍絲既標準對付佢"},{"pid":"2119882a02cf55617aad3ae0a8111455c9fd3d4b","tid":1527280,"uid":136426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:46:57.000Z","msg":"拖走，講經+口頭警告。佢再返去阻，立即拖出去打佢老母臭閪，一路打一路大叫「死阻膠，唔聽警告？打！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反正呢班人，衝又唔夠膽，唔敢擋老黑狗狗剩係擋手足，完全係一個禍害黎。打撚完佢佢嬲又好唱又好乜都好，令佢唔好再係前線再出現就最好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆之原則剩係適用於勇武同和理非，無左膠份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。雖然，有好多左膠聲稱自己係「和理非」，但佢根本唔明咩叫和理非，佢地只係「非」。當有人因為你既大愛而間接地受傷，不論手足定對家，已經唔係和平。係d咁危險既情況下作出d咁低能既判斷，講埋d咩「唔想自己人變到黑警咁」呢d咁中二病既大道理，已經唔係理性。所以佢地只係「非」，無和理既「非」，就即係左膠，大家隨便割。"},{"pid":"d3d970b786f65a422a9feb74507d67df5df81630","tid":1527280,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4615d8f666e45d0c4a1b628958c95af3a775d3ce","tid":1527280,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:50:34.000Z","msg":"不割蓆呀，咁樣好容易變大量清洗自己人"},{"pid":"df75b28f23b528b327c05431454932d5b4cf2a89","tid":1527280,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:51:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1分29秒速龍衝入鐵見人就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到1分40秒佢啲伙計渴班速龍出嚟 入去做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> 由此可見本身落鐵拉人係唔預呢一part發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去到最後同721冇分別</span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以大家一定要集中火力追擊831黑警恐襲太子站旺角站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外5分20秒點解要哄個FA聊個FA出嚟而唔衝入去捉人？<br />\n唯一解釋佢地冇權進入埋架車查 如果唔係上面點會叫返班速龍出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvIau2kwxzZA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=I3kI68XCunzd%2BKkpJ1XxGDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=7013f2a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vIau2kwxzZA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n另外好重要好重要好重要<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoLoCBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoLoCBH.png&h=99a60b07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynKAtJo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynKAtJo.png&h=73eded90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da5ce01f0d7de6318462747e4628dcd30511f7da","tid":1527280,"uid":248373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d00c3bdd7e12e3845f8e14e53ed0e8a36d434d9e","tid":1527280,"uid":113724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:53:57.000Z","msg":"推 比垃圾左膠睇"},{"pid":"c0982c49dc29873aa6f3fd89d8fb023d8596ba3b","tid":1527280,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T20:57:02.000Z","msg":"心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61af5abb9b2a0fb728e6d21c90bb26fe13cab7c","tid":1527280,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:49:02.000Z","msg":"敵人嘅朋友都係敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39adab84cbabc89bf4237560fd026c6d008ef884","tid":1527280,"uid":234704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T21:54:31.000Z","msg":"左膠同勸膠真係好仆街"},{"pid":"2685149b95558339402a5a9f9525b95ba332527c","tid":1527280,"uid":241943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:46:42.000Z","msg":"打暈就停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fe41c68c5ba2631691264bf76a68070f1d9588","tid":1527280,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T22:48:54.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆<br />\n就當係真 你依家同佢地割有乜用先?<br />\n唔好撚分化啦DLLM"},{"pid":"c00974ff2f4c3371686ac6557e7f18d56cdef95c","tid":1527280,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2d003ccdf498bd11882af5200fff47f8a8c2ae","tid":1527280,"uid":252492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5fe41c68c5ba2631691264bf76a68070f1d9588","tid":1527280,"uid":22971,"like":0,"dislik